  "privacy.titulo": "Privacy policy",
  "privacy.cuerpo": "<p><b>{{app}}</b> runs 100&nbsp;% in your browser. We do not send your data to any server.</p><ul><li><b>Data it handles:</b> (a) values you enter, (b) patterns/templates and settings stored locally (IndexedDB/LocalStorage), (c) UI preferences (theme, language, filters, mode).</li><li><b>Local control:</b> you can <b>export</b> or <b>clear local storage</b> anytime. Nothing is deleted outside your device.</li><li><b>Cookies:</b> no tracking cookies or analytics.</li><li><b>Security:</b> your data stays on your device. Avoid sensitive inputs on shared devices.</li><li><b>License & disclaimer:</b> the software is provided “as is”, without warranties.</li></ul><p><b>Author:</b> {{author}}.<br/>Last update: {{updated}}.</p>",

